    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在一个凉爽的夏夜，一场有点神秘的3D解谜冒险等待着你。</strong> <br><strong>帐篷虽然已经搭好……但在这样的满月之夜，好像会发生些什么！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >踏上一场小小的探险之旅吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布所到的峡谷，似乎隐藏着满月之夜的“谜团”……<br>解开谜团的关键在于与路人互动、仔细观察周围环境，并勇敢行动！<br>拿上灯，积极探索吧！ </p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/2225d52c0406677551a3cf1f9f31d1c3.poster.avif?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/2225d52c0406677551a3cf1f9f31d1c3.webm?t=1768750391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >围坐在篝火旁，享受治愈的“咖啡时光”。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >转动磨豆机研磨咖啡豆，在篝火上烧开热水，美味的咖啡即将诞生。<br>可以根据喜好加入牛奶或蜂蜜！向人们分享这温暖的饮品吧。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/8b19319455f2cf7a673c344bf9a1bb81.poster.avif?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/8b19319455f2cf7a673c344bf9a1bb81.webm?t=1768750391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >善用「道具」和「状况」吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破洞的帐篷可以用布片修补。<br>损坏的背负梯可以利用手边的材料进行修理。<br>观察周围的「道具」和「状况」，充分发挥它们的作用！</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/6c4b3f4ed4286da5378033f4c2d3b7d2.poster.avif?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/6c4b3f4ed4286da5378033f4c2d3b7d2.webm?t=1768750391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >放心！本游戏没有恐怖元素！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一提到夜晚探索，大家难免会联想到恐怖游戏。<br>但请放心！这款游戏<strong><u>完全没有恐怖元素。</u></strong><br>拿起手中的灯，照亮黑暗，尽情享受夜晚的探险吧！</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/7fae9ee51a9e43569c38045d5a9222ad.poster.avif?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=263 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/7fae9ee51a9e43569c38045d5a9222ad.webm?t=1768750391\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/9e98c80ece98092b48550c80a6df2ff2.webp?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=20 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于故事的世界观📖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏的世界观来源于开发团队成员Nonohara的著作《ヲかシな建物探访记》，并基于此构建了一个完全原创的故事。<br>因此，即使没有读过本书也完全不影响游戏体验，但如果事先阅读，或者在通关后再读一遍，会让你更加沉浸在布的旅程之中。</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3260830/extras/8c604760a99adc5eafed08fc7f494af8.avif?t=1768750391\" width=616 height=158 /></span>",
